<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>
<simplesect><title>template&lt;typename K, typename V&gt;<?linebreak?>class CustomHashTable&lt; K, V &gt;</title></simplesect>

<para>A custom hash table implementation. </para>



<para>This class provides a custom hash table data structure that allows insertion, lookup, and deletion of key-value pairs.</para>

